CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FA drunken aircraft passenger has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 10 months for his
OL,9,Faggressive and abusive behaviour on a
OL,10,Fflight returning to the UK from Poland.
OL,12,FStephen Blofield, 61, was so
OL,13,Fintoxicated on the Ryanair flight that
OL,14,Fboth crew and fellow holidaymakers
OL,15,Ffeared for their safety.
OL,17,FBristol Crown Court heard how Blofield
OL,18,Fbecame disruptive as the plane
OL,19,Ftravelled from Krakow to Bristol on
OL,20,FNovember 11 last year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FHe had started drinking at the airport
OL,8,Fto calm his nerves ahead of the flight
OL,9,Fand carried on while on board `
OL,10,Fbecoming abusive towards the Polish
OL,11,Fcabin crew.
OL,13,FAs the flight was on approach to
OL,14,FBristol Airport, the British pilot had
OL,15,Fto abort his first attempt at landing
OL,16,Fbecause Blofield refused to sit down
OL,17,Fand fasten his seatbelt. When the
OL,18,Fplane landed, police arrested him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FIan Fenny, prosecuting, said: "When
OL,8,Fthe officers boarded the flight and
OL,9,Fapproached him, they found him to be
OL,10,Fdrunk, aggressive and confrontational.
OL,12,F"Because of the confined space within
OL,13,Fthe fuselage of an aeroplane, they
OL,14,Fwere concerned that he might strike
OL,15,Fout and inflame the situation where
OL,16,Fthey noticed that other passengers
OL,17,Fwere already agitated.
OL,26,@oD@_OUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"Eventually he was arrested and
OL,8,Fhandcuffed and indeed during this
OL,9,Fprocess he struck out, narrowly
OL,10,Fmissing the passenger to his left.
OL,12,F"The principal officer describes the
OL,13,Fdefendant's abuse as effectively the
OL,14,Fworst that he had to endure in 20
OL,15,Fyears as a police officer."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FMr Fenny said Blofield's behaviour was
OL,8,F"so alarming and potentially
OL,9,Fdangerous" that he had to be removed
OL,10,Ffrom the plane using an ambulift,
OL,11,Fwhich is normally reserved for
OL,12,Fdisabled passengers.
OL,14,F"As a consequence of the defendant's
OL,15,Fbehaviour, passengers were effectively
OL,16,Fmarooned on board as the police, and
OL,17,Fmost particularly cabin crew, tried to
OL,18,Fevacuate the plane quietly and
OL,19,Fsafely," Mr Fenny said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@JO]vD@AOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"Because of the defendant's behaviour
OL,8,Fand because of where he was actually
OL,9,Fsitting within the plane, that proved
OL,10,Fvery difficult.
OL,12,F"Thus, a number of the passengers had
OL,13,Fno option but to be further exposed to
OL,14,Fwhat was described by the police as
OL,15,Fthe defendant's vile verbal
OL,16,Faggression."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FAt a previous hearing, Blofield, from
OL,8,FWest Wales, pleaded guilty to being
OL,9,Fdrunk on an aircraft, using
OL,10,Fthreatening or abusive language to
OL,11,Fcabin crew, failing to comply with the
OL,12,Fpilot's instructions, and an offence
OL,13,Funder the Public Order Act of using
OL,14,Fthreatening abusive words or behaviour
OL,15,Flikely to cause harassment, alarm or
OL,16,Fdistress.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FSam Louwers, defending, explained the
OL,8,Fdefendant had lost his medication for
OL,9,Fback pain, depression and anxiety
OL,10,Fahead of the flight to Poland and
OL,11,Fturned to alcohol for the trip home.
OL,13,F"Ultimately, Mr Blofield was a man who
OL,14,Fhas come from a difficult background
OL,15,Fand eventually found himself in Poland
OL,16,Fdue to tracing of family roots," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"When he found himself in Poland
OL,8,Fwithout his medication, he went into a
OL,9,Fform of withdrawal, confining himself
OL,10,Fto his hotel room and decided on that
OL,11,Fbasis that he needed to return to the
OL,12,FUK earlier than planned.
OL,14,F"When he got to the airport, his
OL,15,Fanxiety, depression, pain levels were
OL,16,Fsky high and he became incredibly
OL,17,Fnervous of flying and so foolishly
OL,18,Fdecided that now would be the right
OL,19,Ftime to settle his nerves, as many do,
OL,20,Fwith a drink at the airport."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FHe said the defendant had "no
OL,8,Frecollection" of the incident but had
OL,9,Fseen videos posted on social media of
OL,10,Fhis behaviour.
OL,12,F"He's never denied his behaviour, he's
OL,13,Fnever denied his actions, and as he
OL,14,Fexplained to the police the reason he
OL,15,Fwas struggling so much was because of
OL,16,Fthat medical withdrawal," Mr Louwers
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"Mr Blofield is distressed by his
OL,20,Fbehaviour, he's distressed as to what
OL,21,Fhe has witnessed in these videos.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@MO]tD@AOUxD@YO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"He is also distressed as to the fact
OL,8,Fthat he has found himself before you
OL,9,Ftoday.
OL,11,F"He understands that his behaviour
OL,12,Fcould have easily, and has, disrupted
OL,13,Fother passengers and the airline.
OL,15,F"He understands that it could have
OL,16,Fcaused distress to other people, and
OL,17,Fmost importantly, he understands that
OL,18,Fhis behaviour is nothing short of
OL,19,Funacceptable."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FJudge Euan Ambrose jailed Blofield,
OL,8,Fwho is on benefits and has a lengthy
OL,9,Fcriminal record, for 10 months.
OL,11,F"This is a case where only a custodial
OL,12,Fsentence can be justified," he said.
OL,13,F"It is so serious that no other form
OL,14,Fof sentence would be appropriate.
OL,16,F"You were drunk when you got on board
OL,17,Fand you continued to drink whilst on
OL,18,Fboard, becoming increasingly drunk
OL,19,Fduring the flight.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@[O]uD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"Your behaviour deteriorated, you
OL,8,Fbecame disruptive and aggressive and
OL,9,Frefused to follow basic safety
OL,10,Finstructions from the crew, such as
OL,11,Fbeing asked to sit down, fasten your
OL,12,Fseatbelt and matters of that sort.
OL,14,F"You caused great concern and fear
OL,15,Famongst fellow passengers and also
OL,16,Ffear and alarm to the crew.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"Your behaviour was such that the
OL,8,Ffirst attempt at landing into Bristol
OL,9,Fhad to be aborted and when the plane
OL,10,Ffinally did manage to land, police
OL,11,Fwere called and boarded the plane.
OL,13,F"When they approached you, they found
OL,14,Fyou drunk, aggressive, confrontational
OL,15,Fand extraordinarily abusive towards
OL,16,Fthem."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,FSpeaking after the case, Inspector
OL,8,FChristian Gresswell of Avon and
OL,9,FSomerset Police's Bristol Airport
OL,10,Fpolicing team said passengers have a
OL,11,Fduty to ensure they are fit enough to
OL,12,Ffly and not intoxicated.
OL,14,F"Stephen Blofield caused the initial
OL,15,Flanding to be aborted and continued to
OL,16,Fbe verbally abusive towards cabin
OL,17,Fcrew," he said.
OL,19,F"He was met by officers at Bristol
OL,20,FAirport once the flight had safely
OL,21,Flanded.
OL,26,@vD@AOUyD@FO]{D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"We want people travelling to and from
OL,8,Fa holiday to relax and enjoy
OL,9,Fthemselves, but we hope this case
OL,10,Fserves as a bit of a reminder to
OL,11,Fpeople that everyone needs to take
OL,12,Fresponsibility for their own actions
OL,13,Fand ensure they are in a fit state to
OL,14,Ffly.
OL,16,F"An intoxicated passenger can pose an
OL,17,Funacceptable risk to safety, and
OL,18,Fthat's why we take the offence so
OL,19,Fseriously.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/17
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1775578269
OL,3,CDrunk Ryanair passenger jailed after
OL,4,Cmid-air abuse forced pilot to abort
OL,5,Clanding
OL,7,F"We will continue to work closely with
OL,8,Fairport staff and airlines to keep
OL,9,Fpassengers and crew safe at all times."
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/17
